Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:16.54,DCMain,FANS,0000,0000,0000,,Risa! Risa! Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:20.49,DCMain,FANS,0000,0000,0000,,Risa! Risa! Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:23.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Risa Purple-san is really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:27.53,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. She was originally \Na charismatic underground idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:29.23,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone loves her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:33.28,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's popular to cosplay as her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:39.39,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Her most charming feature is this mole.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:43.42,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,We should thank Kogoro-no-ojisan \Nfor making today happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:50.40,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I know. We were invited because he \Nwas hired to be Risa-san's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:05.25,Risa,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Risa Purple (21)\NIdol
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.25,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I feel like I'm dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:08.31,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe so many people came.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:15.22,Ginji,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Yamane Ginji (38)\NRisa's Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:12.01,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm glad she's gaining more \Nfans, but as her manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:16.80,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm worried some thugs \Nmight try to attack her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:19.10,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:27.16,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I, Mori Kogoro, will protect Risa-san with \Nmy life, no matter who dares to attack her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:29.70,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Bianca, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:30.73,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:32.51,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.20,DCMain,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,Bianca.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:37.20,Bianca,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Bianca (26)\NConcert MC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:37.20,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Risa, let's get this concert started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:40.78,Junichi,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Sakuta Junichi (34)\NBeika Cable TV Director
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:40.78,DCMain,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay, Bianca. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:48.04,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.93,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your MC, Bianca.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:53.05,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:57.80,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's call Risa Purple onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:01.18,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.18,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:09.63,DCMain,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:20.70,DCMain,FANS,0000,0000,0000,,Risa! Risa! Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.92,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:45.85,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:50.77,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Risa-san, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.53,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta, turn on your light!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.32,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.70,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Risa Purple has been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.41,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.04,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.35,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.88,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A canvas stained black with crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,With brilliant detective \Nskills, its color is changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.26,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A woman is kidnapped on a concert stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.15,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But the kidnappers mistakenly \Nabduct Ran-neechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:30.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth with the \Nbody of a child and the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.82,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:18.97,DCEpTitle,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(404,1)}Kogoro's Pursuit of Rage\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:17.78,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Kogoro's Pursuit of Rage, Part One!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.02,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing with my daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:41.15,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Give me back my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.78,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:54.47,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:57.39,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Ran-neechan, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.07,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Your concern won't help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.92,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.55,DCMain,CCONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.56,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:15.81,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.43,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Risa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.73,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.90,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a message\NRan-neechan left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.58,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Is she trying to tell us they \Nmistook her for Risa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:30.30,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's probably a clue to the \Nidentity of the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.82,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnappers couldn't have gone far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:36.20,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,They're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.61,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:51.47,Shop,SHIRT,0000,0000,0000,,Recycling Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.53,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:50.58,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see anyone coming from that dock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.52,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,There should've been two\Nmen and one woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:57.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The men may have been carrying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.79,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, with the purple hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.15,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:06.15,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,They got in a red truck and headed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,A red truck? Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.66,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:13.87,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.96,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.74,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.00,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.61,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.84,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Red truck, red truck...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:47.61,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,So the kidnappers mistook Ran-san for \NRisa-san and kidnapped her instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.19,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:55.12,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,The stage was pitch black, and \NRan-san was cosplaying as Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:08:00.37,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought Risa-chan \Nhad been kidnapped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:07.13,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, it seems someone pulled the \Nfire alarm and turned off the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.13,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.71,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like the light from a stun gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:19.87,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,A stun gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:24.64,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They probably used it to \Nknock Ran-san out and kidnap her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.31,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you work with her agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:32.94,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm Sakuta, a director \Nfor Beika Cable TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:36.67,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I've been filming Risa-chan's events
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:39.33,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,for about five years since \Nshe was an underground idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:44.14,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Could you submit this video to the \Npolice to aid in our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:50.63,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I've already sent it to \Nanother TV station as news material.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:51.55,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:55.05,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,It should be on the news soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:58.26,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.50,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have you indiscreetly \Ntaking the story public.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.06,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,It's Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.43,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.73,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pursuing the kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.57,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:16.82,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,They appeared to have fled in a red truck \Nalong the canal towards the clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:20.33,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Along the canal towards \Nthe clock tower, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.61,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Have we found Ran-kun's phone signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.17,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:29.33,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The car carrying Ran-san is \Ntraveling towards the clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.13,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Call headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:35.26,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Be on the lookout for a red \Ntruck driving along the canal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:36.34,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure, I left Conan at the \Nmotorboat the kidnappers abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:43.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Could you pick him up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.46,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:49.59,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun is at the dock. \NGo pick him up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.73,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:59.91,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnappers were careless enough \Nto accidentally kidnap Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.43,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They must have left some \Nkind of evidence behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.39,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.27,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, the truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:24.05,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,the agency had been receiving\Nthreatening phone calls since last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.52,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Threatening phone calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:30.23,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Someone claiming to be a fan \Ndemanded that we free Risa,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.55,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,and said they felt bad that we \Nmade her work for so little pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:37.65,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,That if nothing changed, something \Nterrible would happen at the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.91,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like they were \Npredicting today's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.55,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.16,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,I have no complaints about the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:51.94,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,We believe it was the \Ndelusion of a maniacal fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.98,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who the kidnappers might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:58.03,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Since Risa debuted \Nas an underground idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.68,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,there's a man who has \Nattended all of her events.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.74,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:07.93,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,there is that suspicious guy who comes \Nto all her photo and handshake events.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.35,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,A suspicious man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:26.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:32.22,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Red truck, red truck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.40,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.22,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just in a hurry since I'm late for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:54.25,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea he was in such a hurry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.62,DCItalic,ANNOUNCER,0000,0000,0000,,This just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:12:03.03,DCItalic,ANNOUNCER,0000,0000,0000,,Someone appears to have been kidnapped\Nfrom idol-singer Risa Purple-san's concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.82,DCItalic,ANNOUNCER,0000,0000,0000,,We received this video of the concert \Njust after the kidnapping occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.03,DCItalic,ANNOUNCER,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:09.78,DCItalic,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:12.79,DCItalic,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Risa Purple has been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:17.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've seen that \Nman somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.67,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Pause. Zoom in on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.43,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,That's him! It's definitely him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:31.47,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.37,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.45,Takichi,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Takeyama Takichi (43)\NRecycling Shop Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.46,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,This is him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.21,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,He's the suspicious man who \Ncomes to all her events.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.17,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you an image of the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.47,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Find out what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:11.60,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:20.90,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,So the kidnapper was riding \Nin the car Mori-san took?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:26.91,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He said Ran-neechan's hair was purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.94,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,There should've been two\Nmen and one woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.91,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The men may have been carrying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.16,DCItalic,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, with the purple hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.42,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:41.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But this had fallen between \Nthe boat and the dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.63,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They probably dropped it while \Nthey were getting off the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:49.98,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,If he were just a witness who had \Nnothing to do with the kidnapping,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:53.93,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,he never would've said her hair was purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.93,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to the message Ran-neechan left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.36,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Message?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.86,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She was trying to write "recycling shop,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:09.61,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,but they must've carried her off the boat \Nafter only managing to write "Risa."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.62,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Recycling shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:17.15,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There was a refrigerator in the \Nback of the recycling truck,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:24.56,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,so the larger man must've trapped \NRan-neechan in there and hidden in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:32.51,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They used something to gag her, so she turned\Non her phone so we'd know where she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:36.77,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's why her signal was \Nmoving towards the clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:40.93,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,There never was any red truck to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.02,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kogoro-no-ojisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:48.88,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency. I figured \Nout who the kidnapper is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.86,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The man driving the recycling truck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:55.79,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What? How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:59.58,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan was trapped inside \Nthe refrigerator in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.28,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Inside the refrigerator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:08.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't believe I didn't realize Ran \Nand the kidnappers were riding with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:12.07,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-san, we can use a GPS \Nto track Ran-san's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.55,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:32.07,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Yosaburo, be gentle with Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.03,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.97,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,What? This isn't Risa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:44.90,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.25,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:48.21,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.97,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who mistook me for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.72,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.86,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.44,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Her cell phone is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.61,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,The police could find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.78,Yosaburo,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Ihara Yosaburo (28)\NRecycling Shop Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.78,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sir, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:20.54,DCMain,YAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Yosaburo, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:23.56,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it, but we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.29,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,She's seen our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.93,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan's phone signal disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.18,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.69,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-san, do you know where they were headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:50.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The car's bumper was dragging along the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow this trail, it \Nshould take us to their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:57.93,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mori-san, then we should take the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.89,DCItalic,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.96,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,We've identified the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.70,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama Takichi, 43 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:09.29,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,He runs a recycling shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:16.01,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,He has only one employee, but he's 190 \Ncentimeters tall and likely his accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.16,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,He's Ihara Yosaburo, 28 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.47,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you the data now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:21.97,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.25,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:36.20,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta-san, we've received a lot of requests \Nfor interviews regarding the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.59,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we return to the agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.41,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.33,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.20,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,You still have more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.19,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I figured out something \Nthat was bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.33,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.44,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,The fire alarm the kidnappers pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:54.65,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,was located in the hallway \Nbetween the stage and greenroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:18:01.47,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Normally the door is locked from the \Nhallway, preventing access from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:08.14,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the kidnappers \Ncouldn't have pulled the fire alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:13.27,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Which means one of us triggered the alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.39,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:19.82,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,When the fire alarm sounded, \Nwe were all onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.38,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:26.25,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Even Risa-san and her manager and \NBianca were recorded by this camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:34.03,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right. One of the kidnappers \Nmust have pulled the fire alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:38.10,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,But if they were able to enter the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:42.05,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,that means the door was unlocked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:45.72,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,So one of us unlocked the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:48.38,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to imagine anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:53.73,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone go out into the hallway \Nbefore the concert began?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:59.40,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, Yamane-san, \Nyou were gone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:02.99,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I just went to make a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.41,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't unlock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.33,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the kidnappers' hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.12,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:28.64,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnappers are crazy \Nfans of Risa Purple-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:36.15,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-san, I received a \Ncall from the inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.69,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper is Takeyama \NTakichi, 43 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:43.16,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The other is his employee Ihara Yosaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:46.16,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,This is him! Takeyama Takichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takeyama's Takichi's Facenet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.44,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Facenet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.17,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Shigaki Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:57.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Shigaki Risa is Risa Purple's real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:20:01.49,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper was exchanging \Ne-mails with Risa Purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:06.12,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,"Takeyama-san, please. Please save me."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:11.08,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"Please take me from the stage \Non the day of the concert?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:15.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,"Pull the fire alarm \Nand cause a commotion?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:19.57,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is a blueprint of the event space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:26.89,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Risa Purple planned this \Nkidnapping and had Takeyama carry it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.63,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:32.83,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Why would an idol work with a fan \Nto create this kind of commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Because it would gain her the \Nattention of all of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.26,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:43.49,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,This incident has been all \Nover TV and the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:48.60,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Risa Purple's name has spread not just among \Nher fans but across the entire nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.46,DCMain,CCONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama responded fifteen minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:57.61,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"Risa-chan, we accidentally kidnapped \Nsome girl we don't recognize."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:59.61,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"What should we do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:02.99,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,If it was an accident, \Nthey should let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.18,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"We're taking the refrigerator \Nto the graveyard."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.99,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"Please call us."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.49,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:16.21,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's a graveyard \Nfor TVs and computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:20.75,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So they abandoned her in a heap of garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:26.76,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They probably planned to release Risa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.68,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll let Ran go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.84,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:37.71,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Since Ran has seen their faces, it's \Nhard to imagine they'll let her live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.78,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The less forethought someone has,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.36,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,the more capable they are of just about \Nanything when they feel cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:48.39,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that means taking someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:27.62,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.20,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.13,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.14,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.59,0:23:40.87,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:24:08.96,DCEpPreview,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.16,0:23:46.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.86,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,We lost our only way to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:51.46,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:55.74,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter surely has no value to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.65,0:24:03.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Though she doesn't tell her father anything, \NI'm sure she dreams of a happy future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:08.96,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And you're trying to take that \Nfuture from her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:14.97,DCNextEp,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoro's Pursuit of Rage\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:14.33,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is "Kogoro's \NPursuit of Rage, Part Two!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:34.99,Hint,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Mole
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.40,0:24:32.18,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.62,0:24:34.33,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A mole!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:36.88,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next time, the old man \Nand I will take them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:39.98,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.88,0:24:37.73,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Will we win big at the races?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.73,0:24:39.62,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's not what I meant.
